{"title":"相信你的智慧（维吾尔族谚语）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":12,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"相信你的智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（维吾尔族谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与其相信你的金钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒不如相信你的智慧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与其寻找金钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒不如寻找智慧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糊涂虫哪儿知道贤明者的宝贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健康人哪儿知道病患者的痛苦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸耀自己是一个糊涂虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸耀妻子是两个糊涂虫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵世杰选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}